# 1. Basic listing
Options +Indexes

# 2. Modern settings (VersionSort handles 1.10 correctly)
IndexOptions FancyIndexing HTMLTable VersionSort NameWidth=* SuppressDescription SuppressHTMLPreamble

# 3. Hide the system files
IndexIgnore .htaccess header.html footer.html

# 4. Inject the header and footer
HeaderName header.html
ReadMeName footer.html

# 5. Tell the server that subfolders should open index.html
DirectoryIndex index.html